snippet.title: Dead Cells coming to console in 2018!
snippet.description:
Dead Cells is coming to your favourite console in 2018! Well maybe not to Ouya, but it will be available on Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4 and the Xbox One.

Release Date announcement will come later in the year.

Get it now on PC here: 
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/588650/Dead_Cells/
GoG: https://www.gog.com/game/dead_cells
Humble: https://www.humblebundle.com/store/dead-cells
